title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861.
author: Victoria
snippet: We started about ten minutes past eleven, andproceeded exactly as last year, fording the Geldieat first very frequently.

title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861.
author: Victoria
snippet: We mounted at once, and rode upalong the Geldie, which we had to ford frequentlyto avoid the bogs, and rode on for two hours upGhn Geldie, over a moor which was so soft andboggy in places that we had to get off severaltimes.
